               <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Remove the system-tray icon entirely. With no tray to restore from, closing the window then quits the app instead of hiding it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
