              <property name="toolTip">
               <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Blurs your chats until you hover over them, so someone glancing at the screen cannot read them. Hovering a row reveals just that row.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
