              <property name="toolTip">
               <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;Recolours WhatsApp Web itself. Photos, avatars and stickers keep their own colours. Works on top of the light or dark theme, whichever is active.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
